bound cloud traffic at the router via a firewall rule.\n\nIntegrate Frigate into PAN — on detection events Frigate fires JSON payloads, PAN ingests them as a sensor data source (camera detections, clips, timestamps). Fits the existing PAN biosensor/data silo aggregation architecture.\n\nNo NVR hardware, no subscriptions, no Chinese cloud, all footage stays on TedProDesk1.","status":"todo","priority":1,"sort_order":26,"created_at":"2026-04-02 19:12:53","completed_at":null,"org_id":"org_personal"},{"id":61,"project_id":791,"milestone_id":5,"title":"App restrictions / blocklist","description":null,"status":"todo","priority":0,"sort_order":0,"created_at":"2026-03-23 11:42:05","completed_at":null,"org_id":"org_personal"},{"id":309,"project_id":791,"milestone_id":5,"title":"Chat shows only bookend events — need intermediate responses visible","description":null,"status":"done","priority":1,"sort_order":0,"created_at":"2026-03-24 21:08:36","completed_at":"2026-04-13 17:12:12","org_id":"org_personal"},{"id":340,"project_id":791,"milestone_id":5,"title":"Smart scroll — remember exact scroll position, restore on every refresh/update/tool call","description":null,"status":"done","priority":1,"sort_order":0,"created_at":"2026-03-24 21:55:10","completed_at":"2026-04-13 17:12:52","org_id":"org_personal"},{"id":310,"project_id":791,"milestone_id":5,"title":"Terminal scroll still janky — jumps on tool calls","description":null,"status":"done","priority":1,"sort_order":0,"created_at":"2026-03-24 21:08:36","completed_at":"2026-04-13 17:19:58","org_id":"org_personal"},{"id":366,"project_id":791,"milestone_id":5,"title":"Transcript messages disappear on refresh","description":null,"status":"backlog","priority":0,"sort_order":0,"created_at":"2026-04-01 20:52:03","completed_at":null,"org_id":"org_personal"},{"id":62,"project_id":791,"milestone_id":5,"title":"Browser separation config","description":null,"status":"todo","priority":0,"sort_order":1,"created_at":"2026-03-23 11:42:05","compl